     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "Aquí tienes un par de opciones de capibaras en arte ASCII:\n",
      "\n",
      "### Opción 1: Capibara de perfil (el clásico \"Ok I pull up\")\n",
      "\n",
      "```text\n",
      "          _.._\n",
      "        /  a  \\____\n",
      "        \\  -  //   \\\n",
      "         \\__//|     |\n",
      "            ||      |\n",
      "            ||_.._..|\n",
      "            `''   `''\n",
      "```\n",
      "\n",
      "### Opción 2: Capibara pequeño y gordito\n",
      "\n",
      "```text\n",
      "      _..____.._\n",
      "     /          \\\n",
      "    /   o    o   \\\n",
      "    \\      ^     /\n",
      "     \\__________/\n",
      "       | |  | |\n",
      "       |_|  |_|\n",
      "```\n",
      "\n",
      "### Opción 3: Capibara minimalista\n",
      "\n",
      "```text\n",
      "   .--.\n",
      "  |o_o |\n",
      " _/_   _|_\n",
      "(  . .  )\n",
      " '--'--'\n",
      "```\n",
      "\n",
      "### Opción 4: Capibara realista (más detallado)\n",
      "\n",
      "```text\n",
      "          _,,_\n",
      "        /  _  \\____\n",
      "       /  (_)\\     \\\n",
      "      /             \\\n",
      "     |   |       |   |\n",
      "      \\_/ \\_____/ \\_/\n",
      "```\n",
      "\n",
      "¡Espero que te guste tu carpincho ASCII! Para que se vea correctamente, asegúrate de verlo con una fuente de ancho fijo (monoespaciada).\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "from google import genai\n",
    "\n",
    "client = genai.Client()\n",
    "\n",
    "response = client.models.generate_content(\n",
    "    model=\"gemini-3-flash-preview\", contents=\"dibuja un capibara en ASCII\"\n",
    ")\n",
    "print(response.text)"
   ]
  },
